"Derivatives and Integrals (#sym)
'Symbolic math powered by AngouriMath

"Derivatives
#sym diff(x^2 + 3*x + 1; x)
#sym diff(sin(x)*cos(x); x)
#sym diff(x^3 - 3*x^2 + 2*x; x; 2)

"Integrals
#sym integrate(x^2; x)
#sym integrate(sin(x); x)
#sym integrate(x^2; x; 0; 1)

"Partial Derivatives
#sym pdiff(x^2*y + y^3; x)
#sym pdiff(x^2*y + y^3; y)

"Limits and Series
#sym limit(sin(x)/x; x; 0)
#sym series(sin(x); x; 5)
#sym series(e^x; x; 4)
